import React from 'react'
import styled from 'styled-components'

function ChatInfo() {
    return (
        <Container>
            <InputContainer>
                <form>
                    <input type="text" placeholder="Enter your Message here..."/>
                </form>
            </InputContainer>
        </Container>
    )
}

export default ChatInfo
const Container = styled.div`
background: orange;`
const InputContainer = styled.div`
 `
